videos.description: Seton Hall's Michael Nzei powers in a two-handed slam with the foul after good ball movement.
videos.headline: Nzei slams the ball plus a foul

videos.description: URI's Fatts Russell loses his balance but still finishes lay-in on the fast break.
videos.headline: Russell makes acrobatic layup

videos.description: Seton Hall's Myles Cale catches an outlet pass and abuses the rim with a massive dunk.
videos.headline: Cale rocks the rim in transition

videos.description: URI's Ryan Preston chases down Myles Powell for the monster block on the fast break.
videos.headline: Preston swats Powell from behind

videos.description: URI's Jared Terrell weaves the ball through the Seton Hall defense with one hand while in the air to complete a difficult lay-in.
videos.headline: Terrell makes the up-and-under scoop layup

videos.description: Seton Hall's Desi Rodriguez swerves around a defender while jumping towards the basket on the fast break.
videos.headline: Rodriguez's steal turns into circus layup

videos.description: Seton Hall's Khadeen Carrington puts a URI defender on skates en route to a fade away jumper.
videos.headline: Carrington puts on a dribbling clinic to set up jumper

videos.description: URI stuns No. 20 Seton Hall in the final seconds with a Jared Terrell fall-away floater.
videos.headline: Terrell wins it in the final seconds for URI

videos.description: Rhode Island's Jared Terrell puts up a career high 32 points and leads the way for his team's upset win over No. 20 Seton Hall.
videos.headline: Jared Terrell's career night paves way in URI's upset victory over Seton Hall
